object.script:
prN=property.getNumber prB=property.getBool rps = prN('Radar RPS') Rad1 = prN('Search Range 1 (m)') Rad2 = prN('Search Range 2 (m)') Rad3 = prN('Search Range 3 (m)') Rad4 = prN('Search Range 4 (m)') MaxTrgtNum = prN('Maximum Target Number') FOV = prN('Radar FOV') pi2 = 2*math.pi DispMode, CurYaw, TrgNum = 0, 0, 1 Pressed, Pressed_old = false, false TgX, TgY, TgZ, Mas, Dec = {}, {}, {}, {}, {} linewidth = 16 scrXofst = 2
function onTick() inN=input.getNumber inB=input.getBool TrgDst=inN(1) TrgPit=inN(2) TrgStr=inN(3) GPSX=inN(4) GPSY=inN(5) Alt=inN(6) Pitch=inN(7) Comp=inN(8) inX=inN(9) inY=inN(10) dispDir=inN(11) detR=inN(12) Det=inB(1) isPr=inB(2) act=inB(3) DSR=inB(4) DC=inB(5) CUT=inB(6)
if (-0.25 <= Comp and Comp < 0.5) then OriX = Comp + 0.25 else OriX = Comp + 1.25 end
function Pulse(Pressed,Pressed_old) if(Pressed and not Pressed_old) then Pulse = true return Pulse end end
function sin2p(x) return math.sin(x*pi2) end function cos2p(x) return math.cos(x*pi2) end
if Pulse(isPr, isPr_old) then DispMode = DispMode + 1 if DispMode == 4 then DispMode = 0 end end
if DispMode == 0 then Rad = Rad1 elseif DispMode == 1 then Rad = Rad2 elseif DispMode == 2 then Rad = Rad3 elseif DispMode == 3 then Rad = Rad4 end
isPr_old = isPr
if #Mas>0 then for i=1,#Mas do Dec[i] = Dec[i] - rps/60 if Dec[i] < 0 then Dec[0] = 0 end end end
if Det and TrgDst > detR then TgX[TrgNum]=GPSX+TrgDst*cos2p(OriX-CurYaw) TgY[TrgNum]=GPSY+TrgDst*sin2p(OriX-CurYaw) TgZ[TrgNum]=Alt +TrgDst*math.tan((Pitch + TrgPit)*pi2) Mas[TrgNum]=TrgStr*TrgDst Dec[TrgNum]=1 TrgNum = TrgNum % MaxTrgtNum + 1 end
CurYaw = CurYaw % 1 + rps/60 if CurYaw>0.5 then CurYaw = CurYaw-1 end
output.setNumber(1, CurYaw) output.setNumber(2, FOV) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() r = h/2 setC=screen.setColor drawT=screen.drawText drawL=screen.drawLine --Display search range if DSR then setC(255, 255, 255, 128) drawT(0+scrXofst, h*0.8, "R") drawT(25+scrXofst, h*0.8, "M") if Rad >= 1000 then drawT(5+scrXofst, h*0.8, math.floor(Rad)) else drawT(10+scrXofst, h*0.8, math.floor(Rad)) end end
--Display radar setC(0, 255, 0) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, r) if act then drawL(w/2, h/2, w/2+r*cos2p(CurYaw-0.25), h/2+r*sin2p(CurYaw-0.25)) for i=1,linewidth do setC(0, 255*(1-i/(linewidth+1)), 0, 255*(1-i/(linewidth+1))) drawL(w/2, h/2, w/2+r*cos2p(CurYaw-0.25-i*rps/60), h/2+r*sin2p(CurYaw-0.25-i*rps/60)) end for i=1,#Mas do trsi=255*Dec[i] if CUT then if Mas[i]==60500 then setC(255,0,0,trsi) elseif Mas[i]==500 then setC(255,127,0,trsi) elseif Mas[i]==400 then setC(0,127,255,trsi) elseif Mas[i]==30 then setC(255,255,255,trsi) else setC(0,255,0,trsi) end else setC(0,255,0,trsi) end dX = TgX[i] - GPSX dY = TgY[i] - GPSY TrgDsti = ((dX)^2 + (dY)^2)^(1 / 2) m = dY / dX --calculate Orientation against X axis if (dX > 0 and dY >= 0) then TrgOriX = math.atan(m) / pi2 elseif (dX > 0 and dY <0) then TrgOriX = math.atan(m) / pi2 + 1 elseif (dX < 0) then TrgOriX = math.atan(m) / pi2 + 0.5 elseif (dX == 0 and dY > 0) then TrgOriX = 0.25 elseif (dX == 0 and dY < 0) then TrgOriX = 0.75 elseif (dX == 0 and dY == 0) then TrgOriX = 0 end --calculate Deviation of Orientation TrgOri = OriX - TrgOriX if (TrgOri > 0.4) then TrgOri = TrgOri - 1 elseif (TrgOri < -0.5) then TrgOri = TrgOri + 1 end angle = TrgOri-0.25 if TrgDsti/Rad < 0.46 then screen.drawRectF(w/2+(w/2*TrgDsti/Rad)*cos2p(angle), h/2+(h/2*TrgDsti/Rad)*sin2p(angle), 1, 1) end end end
--Display north and south if DC then NAng = OriX + dispDir + 0.5 SAng = NAng + 0.5 setC(255, 0, 0) drawL(w/2+(r-2)*cos2p(NAng), h/2+(r-2)*sin2p(NAng),w/2+(r+2)*cos2p(NAng), h/2+(r+2)*sin2p(NAng)) setC(0, 0, 255) drawL(w/2+(r-2)*cos2p(SAng), h/2+(r-2)*sin2p(SAng),w/2+(r+2)*cos2p(SAng), h/2+(r+2)*sin2p(SAng)) end end

object.script:
pi=math.pi pi2=2*pi inN=input.getNumber inB=input.getBool s=math.sin c=math.cos t=math.tan at=math.atan abs=math.abs min=math.min drawT=screen.drawText drawL=screen.drawLine drawR=screen.drawRect setC=screen.setColor form=string.format function sgn(x) if x==0 then return 0 else return x/abs(x) end end function devAng(q,q0,qt,cw) return -cw*(q-q0+(1-qt))%1-(1-qt) end function updnText(x,posX,posY,xRange,xPitch,xScale,scale,label) if label then drawT(posX,posY-2,form("%3.0f",x)) drawR(posX-2,posY-4, 17, 8) end if scale then for i=0,math.floor(xRange/(xPitch/xScale)) do xmod=x%xPitch xint=i*xPitch if (xmod-xint)*xScale<-7 and (xmod-xint)*xScale>-30 then drawT(posX,posY+(xmod-xint)*xScale,form("%3.0f",x-xmod+xint)) end if (xmod+xint)*xScale>5 and (xmod+xint)*xScale<30 then drawT(posX,posY+(xmod+xint)*xScale,form("%3.0f",x-xmod-xint)) end end end end
function onTick() altunit=inN(9) alt=inN(1)*altunit Vunit=inN(10) dirV=inN(2)*Vunit horV=inN(3)*Vunit verV=inN(4)*Vunit rol0=inN(5) pit0=inN(6) vtilt=inN(7) rol=rol0-min(0,sgn(vtilt))*(sgn(rol0)*0.5-2*rol0) pit=pit0 comp=devAng(inN(8),0,1,1) r=inN(11) ladSc=inN(12) cOpt=inN(13) ss=inB(3) sl=inB(4) as=inB(5) al=inB(6) cs=inB(7) cl=inB(8) vv=inB(9) ll=inB(10) absV=(dirV^2+horV^2+verV^2)^0.5 end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() setC(0,0,0,255) screen.drawClear()
--compass if cOpt == 0 then setC(0, 255, 0) else setC(255, 0, 0) end if cl then drawT(w/2-6,h-7,form("%3.0f",comp*360)) drawR(w/2-8,h-9, 17, 8) drawL(w/2,h-9,w/2,h-17) end if cs then for i=0,35 do angYaw = devAng(i*10/360,comp,0.5,1) if abs(angYaw)<at(w/3/r)/pi2 then drawL(w/2+r*t(angYaw*pi2), h-11, w/2+r*t(angYaw*pi2), h-17) if cl then cRange=at(11/r)/pi2 else cRange=0 end if abs(angYaw)>cRange then drawT(w/2+r*t(angYaw*pi2)-4,h-7,form("%2.0f",(36-i)%36)) end end end end --velocity updnText(absV,2,h/2-10,20,5,2.5,ss,sl) --altitude updnText(alt,w-16,h/2-10,20,5,2.5,as,al) end

dNum = 72 vvSiz=2 pi=math.pi pi2=2*pi inN=input.getNumber inB=input.getBool s=math.sin c=math.cos t=math.tan at=math.atan abs=math.abs min=math.min drawT=screen.drawText drawL=screen.drawLine drawR=screen.drawRect setC=screen.setColor form=string.format function sgn(x) if x==0 then return 0 else return x/abs(x) end end function devAng(q,q0,qt,cw) return -cw*(q-q0+(1-qt))%1-(1-qt) end function rotV2Z(x,y,qz) qz=qz*pi2 return x*c(qz)-y*s(qz),x*s(qz)+y*c(qz) end function drawLineP(x,y,lenO,lenI,angP,angR,angL,label) capL=3 hP=r*t(angP*pi2) if angL<0 then spaceN=3 else spaceN=0 end for i=0,spaceN do int=(lenO-lenI)/(4*spaceN+2) xl1,yl1=rotV2Z(-lenO/2+int*2*i,-hP,-angR) xl2,yl2=rotV2Z(-lenO/2+int*(2*i+1),-hP,-angR) xr1,yr1=rotV2Z(lenO/2-int*2*i,-hP,-angR) xr2,yr2=rotV2Z(lenO/2-int*(2*i+1),-hP,-angR) drawL(x+xl1,y+yl1,x+xl2,y+yl2) drawL(x+xr1,y+yr1,x+xr2,y+yr2) if i==0 then xcl,ycl=rotV2Z(-lenO/2,-hP+sgn(angL)*capL,-angR) xcr,ycr=rotV2Z(lenO/2,-hP+sgn(angL)*capL,-angR) drawL(x+xl1,y+yl1,x+xcl,y+ycl) drawL(x+xr1,y+yr1,x+xcr,y+ycr) end if label then xang,yang=rotV2Z(sgn(vtilt)*(lenO/2+3),-hP-sgn(vtilt)*2,-angR) drawT(x+xang,y+yang,form("%3.0f",angL*360)) end end end
function onTick() altunit=inN(9) alt=inN(1)*altunit Vunit=inN(10) dirV=inN(2)*Vunit horV=inN(3)*Vunit verV=inN(4)*Vunit rol0=inN(5) pit0=inN(6) vtilt=inN(7) rol=rol0-min(0,sgn(vtilt))*(sgn(rol0)*0.5-2*rol0) pit=pit0 comp=devAng(inN(8),0,1,1) r=inN(11) ladSc=inN(12) cOpt=inN(13) ss=inB(3) sl=inB(4) as=inB(5) al=inB(6) cs=inB(7) cl=inB(8) vv=inB(9) ll=inB(10) absV=(dirV^2+horV^2+verV^2)^0.5 vP0=(50/3.6)*Vunit --vv display switch velocity vH0=(1/3.6)*Vunit --vv circle position velocity end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight()
--pitch ladder drawL(w/2-w*ladSc/4,h/2,w/2-2*vvSiz,h/2) drawL(w/2+w*ladSc/4,h/2,w/2+2*vvSiz,h/2) drawL(w/2,h/2-w*ladSc/4,w/2,h/2-2*vvSiz) drawL(w/2,h/2+w*ladSc/4,w/2,h/2+2*vvSiz) setC(0,255,0) for i=1,dNum do angDisp=devAng((i-1)/dNum,0,0.5,-1) angi=devAng(angDisp-pit,0,0.5,-1) if cs and cl then lRange=at((h/2-17)/r)/pi2 else lRange=at((h*3/4)/r)/pi2 end if abs(angi)<lRange then drawLineP(w/2,h/2,w*ladSc,w*ladSc/2,angi,rol,angDisp,ll) end end
--velocity vector if vv then if abs(dirV)>vP0 then vvx=w/2+r*horV/dirV vvy=h/2-r*verV/dirV screen.drawCircle(vvx,vvy,vvSiz) drawL(vvx+vvSiz,vvy,vvx+vvSiz*3,vvy) drawL(vvx-vvSiz,vvy,vvx-vvSiz*3,vvy) drawL(vvx,vvy-vvSiz,vvx,vvy-vvSiz*2) else vvx=w/2--+r*horV/v0 vvy=h/2---r*verV/v0 screen.drawCircleF(vvx,vvy,vvSiz) screen.drawCircle(vvx,vvy,vvSiz*2) fpmRad=(dirV^2+horV^2)^0.5/vH0*2*vvSiz fpmAng=at(dirV/horV)/pi2 fpmx=vvx+horV/vH0 fpmy=vvy-dirV/vH0 drawL(vvx,vvy,fpmx,fpmy) end end end

object.script: -- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 150) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 14) -- Draw a 14px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 7) -- Draw a 7px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 2) -- Draw a 2px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawLine(0, h/2, w, h/2) -- Draw a horizontal line through the center of the screen screen.drawLine(w/2, 0, w/2, h) -- Draw a vertical line through the center of the screen end
